"consist of eight or fewer, all lower case characters in order to maintain "
"backwards compatibility with applications."
msgstr ""
"用户名称在 `login:` 提示符后键入。每个用户必须有一个唯一的用户名。创建有效用户名有一些规则，这些规则在 man:passwd[5] "
