#. type: Title ===
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:618
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Managing Groups"
msgstr ""
"管理群组\n"
"\n"
"== Creating a Group\n"
"\n"
"To create a group, you can use the command line or a graphical user interface tool. With command line, you can use the \"addgroup\" command followed by the group name. For example, to create a group called \"developers\", you can use the following command:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"addgroup developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"With a graphical user interface tool, you can typically find an option to create a group in the system settings or administrative tools.\n"
"\n"
"== Modifying a Group\n"
"\n"
"To modify a group, you can use the \"groupmod\" command followed by the group name. For example, to change the name of a group from \"developers\" to \"programmers\", you can use the following command:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"groupmod -n programmers developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"You can also modify other properties of a group, such as its ID or membership.\n"
"\n"
"== Deleting a Group\n"
"\n"
"To delete a group, you can use the \"groupdel\" command followed by the group name. For example, to delete the group called \"developers\", you can use the following command:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"groupdel developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Deleting a group will also remove all the users that are associated with it, so use this command with caution.\n"
"\n"
"== Managing Group Membership\n"
"\n"
"To add a user to a group, you can use the \"usermod\" command followed by the \"-aG\" option and the group name. For example, to add a user called \"john\" to the group \"developers\", you can use the following command:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"usermod -aG developers john\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"To remove a user from a group, you can use the \"gpasswd\" command followed by the \"-d\" option and the username. For example, to remove the user \"john\" from the group \"developers\", you can use the following command:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"gpasswd -d john developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"== Viewing Group Information\n"
"\n"
"To view information about a group, you can use the \"groupmod\" command followed by the \"-o\" option and the group name. For example, to view detailed information about the group \"developers\", you can use the following command:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"groupmod -o developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"You can also use the \"grep\" command to search for specific information about a group in the \"/etc/group\" file. For example, to search for all groups that a user called \"john\" belongs to, you can use the following command:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"grep john /etc/group\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"这里是有关群组管理的一些内容。\n"
"\n"
"== 创建群组\n"
"\n"
"创建群组可以使用命令行或图形用户界面工具。使用命令行，您可以使用\"addgroup\"命令后跟群组名称来创建群组。例如，要创建一个名为\"developers\"的群组，可以使用以下命令：\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"addgroup developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"使用图形用户界面工具，通常可以在系统设置或管理工具中找到创建群组的选项。\n"
"\n"
"== 修改群组\n"
"\n"
"要修改群组，可以使用\"groupmod\"命令后跟群组名称。例如，要将群组名称从\"developers\"更改为\"programmers\"，可以使用以下命令：\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"groupmod -n programmers developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"您还可以修改群组的其他属性，如其ID或成员身份。\n"
"\n"
"== 删除群组\n"
"\n"
"要删除群组，可以使用\"groupdel\"命令后跟群组名称。例如，要删除名为\"developers\"的群组，可以使用以下命令：\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"groupdel developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"删除群组也将删除与之关联的所有用户，因此请谨慎使用此命令。\n"
"\n"
"== 管理群组成员身份\n"
"\n"
"要将用户添加到群组中，可以使用\"usermod\"命令后跟\"-aG\"选项和群组名称。例如，要将名为\"john\"的用户添加到群组\"developers\"中，可以使用以下命令：\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"usermod -aG developers john\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"要将用户从群组中移除，可以使用\"gpasswd\"命令后跟\"-d\"选项和用户名。例如，要将用户\"john\"从群组\"developers\"中移除，可以使用以下命令：\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"gpasswd -d john developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"== 查看群组信息\n"
"\n"
"要查看有关群组的信息，可以使用\"groupmod\"命令后跟\"-o\"选项和群组名称。例如，要查看有关群组\"developers\"的详细信息，可以使用以下命令：\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"groupmod -o developers\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"您还可以使用\"grep\"命令在\"/etc/group\"文件中搜索有关群组的特定信息。例如，要搜索用户\"john\"所属的所有群组，可以使用以下命令：\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"grep john /etc/group\n"
"```"

